title: Fox Presents: Damo’s Indo Revival
description:
Deep bottom turns and even deeper barrels, Damien Hobgood goes haywire in surfing’s hallowed archipelago…and reminds the Fox Youth Brigade why he’s the legend that he is. 

Music: "Boogieshuttle" by Hobosexual 





Filmed and Edited by : Jensen Young Sik
